author: Epic Games
description:
Welcome to Albion, Governor!  
Discover these mysterious Celtic wetlands, where no civilized Roman wants to be. From architectural styles to which deities to worship, the degree to which you Romanize your provinces is up to you. Will you embrace local Celtic culture or impose Roman traditions? The fate of this region—and your legacy—is yours to decide. 

Anno 117: Pax Romana is available November 13, 2025 📜 
Pre-purchase now 👉 https://epic.gm/anno117
title: Anno 117: Pax Romana | Official Albion Trailer

author: Epic Games
description:
The next chapter in the Hell Let Loose franchise; Hell Let Loose: Vietnam, is launching in 2026.

Step into the intense, large-scale battles of the Vietnam War with 50vs50 combat, historically accurate maps, and fresh gameplay systems designed around brutal jungle warfare.
This isn’t just a game. It’s a hardcore, immersive theatre of war like no other.

Are you ready to fight? Wishlist now on the Epic Games Store! https://epic.gm/hllv
title: Hell Let Loose: Vietnam | Reveal Trailer

author: Epic Games
description:
Where Winds Meet will be released on November 14, 2025 on the Epic Games Store!
 
Where Winds Meet is an epic open-world action-adventure RPG rooted in the rich legacy of Wuxia. The story is set in the turbulent era of tenth-century China, and you'll take on the role of a young sword master, uncovering forgotten truths and the mysteries of your own identity. 
As the wind sweeps over mountains and rivers, your legend will unfold.
 
Wishlist now: https://epic.gm/where-winds-meet
title: Where Winds Meet | Release Date Trailer
